  "knowledge_nodes": [
    {
      "content": "真空是完全没有阻力的介质（介质密度为零）。",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "setting",
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_8e103b188b7e09fc",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "setting.vacuum",
          "module": "default",
          "package": "galileo_fine",
          "version": "4.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "斜面沟槽经抛光处理，衬以羊皮纸，使用坚硬光滑的青铜球——摩擦和空气阻力可忽略。",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "setting",
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_dac4550741639edb",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "setting.plane",
          "module": "default",
          "package": "galileo_fine",
          "version": "4.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "日常生活中，石头比羽毛下落更快，铁球比木球更快。",
      "kind": "observation",
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "metadata": {
        "prior": 0.9
      },
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_5469fe65fe36d61a",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "obs.daily",
          "module": "default",
          "package": "galileo_fine",
          "version": "4.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "在不同介质中比较轻重物体的下落，介质越稠密速度差异越明显；越稀薄差异越不明显。",
      "kind": "observation",
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "metadata": {
        "prior": 0.9
      },
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_e384821b08ebd7f4",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "obs.media",
          "module": "default",
          "package": "galileo_fine",
          "version": "4.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "在空气中，金球、铅球、铜球等重材料球从100腕尺落下，金球领先铜球不超过四指。",
      "kind": "observation",
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "metadata": {
        "prior": 0.9
      },
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_10d06d805e009860",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "obs.air",
          "module": "default",
          "package": "galileo_fine",
          "version": "4.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "斜面实验1：不同重量的球沿抛光沟槽滚下，所经距离之比等于时间之比的平方，与球重量无关。",
      "kind": "observation",
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "metadata": {
        "prior": 0.9
      },
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_4f7a2aa878003c5e",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "obs.theta1",
          "module": "default",
          "package": "galileo_fine",
          "version": "4.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "斜面实验2：重复实验百余次，结果偏差不超过脉搏一次，高度可重复。",
      "kind": "observation",
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "metadata": {
        "prior": 0.9
      },
      "parameters": [],
