    {
      "content": "假设重物下落更快，将重球H与轻球L绑在一起，L拖拽H，复合体HL速度应慢于H。",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_a411fb301c436f80",
      "source_refs": [
